{
  "stem": "4247.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while I was Jewish, I went to Jewish synagogues, and I-- I didn't go to school on main Jewish holidays, I was a person who was reciting [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] nationalistic poems during the school holidays in the school because I was good at that.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my parents came along.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were very, very happy to see me performing in front of 600 children and the-- and the professors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very proud of it, and I was very pleased that I could please them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my background.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what is interesting that when the change started to come, and that started to come from when the first anti-Jewish laws came into being.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then-- then gradually, this-- this Jewish-- this-- this Hungarian background, rather, was slowly pushed into the background.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was starting to-- to search myself, to query the situation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I looked into the mirror and I thought to myself, gee, I must be a pretty awful person if what I can hear from the official papers and-- and all other medias is true.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look, the-- the first Jewish-- anti-Jewish law, it was a very systematic, constitutional issue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It has been-- has been carried by the Hungarian parliament by a majority, a very sizable majority.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, you must understand the political global-- I mean, European global background to it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in return for that, Hungary obtained certain preferential treatment, by which I mean that the detached parts of Hungary, which were a sore point, as I said earlier, in a Hungarian historical mind, were reattached back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because of that, of course, Hungary was quasi-rewarded, right, for towing the German line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was delirious when-- when the northern part of Hungary returned.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
